She say it to the date September 11 and the attack on the World Trade Center, stated that "brothers Americans will be hit by the attack of the steel birds. So what awaits us in the near and not so near future?[/center]

Global cooling. 2221 - People make direct contact with extraterrestrial beings. 2256 - spacecraft carries a new dangerous virus on earth. 2262 - gradually changing the orbits of the planets. Mars is threatened by a comet. 2271 - re-calculated the revised constants. 2273 - The human race is only one race. 2279 - Power from nothing (probably from vacuum or black holes). 2288 - Traveling in time. New encounters with extraterrestrial civilizations. 2291 - The sun goes out. Trying to recover the fusion processes. 2296 - Changes to the gravitational field caused by powerful explosions on the sun. Began to fall old satellites and other space objects. 2299 - In France, the partisan movement emerged against Islam. 2302 - Found new important laws and secrets of the universe. (favorite!) 2304 - Open the secret of the moon. 2341 - Something terrible is approaching Earth. 2354 - Accident of an artificial sun on Earth. Drought. 2371 - Great Famine. 2378 - Fast growing race. 2480 - Two of artificial suns face. Earth is in darkness. 3005 - War on Mars. 3010 - Comet hits Moon. 3797 - At that time life on earth disappears, but humanity will be able to lay the foundations for their survival on other star systems.[/b]
